data.description: WOW!! Check out this OPEN FLOOR PLAN home with 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom, with beautiful wood flooring throughout the lower level and cool grey tones. This home features a kitchen island with beautiful granite countertops that compliments the wood flooring. Oversized bedroom downstairs. Primary bedroom is located upstairs with two closets!! Secondary bedrooms connected by jack and jill bathroom. Enjoy your backyard under the covered patio or finished turf area that features a gondola fire pit. Home is complete with solar and is located within a quite gated community just minutes from Aliante living! Bring your toothbrush and bags, this home is turn key!!
